    <div class="footer">
      <h3>Scoring Instructions</h3>
      <p>Each of the 22 items is scored 0–3: (0 = Never, 1 = Sometimes, 2 = Often, 3 = Always).</p>
      <p>Item 22 ("I feel supported by my family or friends regarding this condition.") is reverse-scored: record it as (0 =&gt; 3), (1 =&gt; 2), (2 =&gt; 1), (3 =&gt; 0) when computing the total.</p>
      <p><strong>Total Score Range:</strong> 0 to 66 — Higher scores indicate greater psychosocial burden due to vitiligo.</p>
